rsation%20on%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FSushantBSinha%2Fstatus%2F1841702235459178617%5C%22%3E%20'Top%20Angle%20With%20Sushant%20Sinha'%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Babita%20Phogat%2C%20daughter%20of%20Mahavir%20Phogat%20and%20former%20India%20wrestler%2C%20opened%20up%20about%20how%20much%20Mahavir%20fought%20to%20preserve%20Vinesh's%20career%20and%20accused%20her%20cousin%20of%20not%20thanking%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20seen%20my%20father%20cry%20just%20three%20times%20in%20my%20life.%20First%2C%20when%20me%20and%20my%20sisters%20got%20married.%20Second%2C%20when%20my%20uncle%20died%20and%20third%2C%20when%20Vinesh%20got%20disqualified%20from%20the%20Olympics%2C%26quot%3B%20Babita%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20my%20uncle%20died%2C%20Vinesh%20and%20both%20of%20her%20siblings%20suddenly%20quit%20wrestling.%20My%20father%20went%20to%20their%20house%20and%20fought%20with%20their%20mother%20to%20get%20them%20back%20to%20wrestling.%20Imagine%20how%20much%20he%20has%20worked%20to%20make%20Vinesh.%20But%20she%20thanked%20everyone%20except%20for%20that%20guru%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20India%20wrestler%20remarked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20National%20Anti-Doping%20Authority%20(NADA)%20has%20served%20a%20notice%20for%20a%20whereabouts%20failure%20to%20retired%20wrestler%C2%A0Vinesh%C2%A0Phogat%20after%20sending%20a%20team%20to%20collect%20urine%20sample%20of%20the%20wrestler%20who%20missed%20a%20medal%20in%20the%20Paris%20Olympic%20Games%20as%20she%20was%20disqualified%20for%20being%20100gms%20overweight%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20the%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notice%20informed%20that%20a%20Dope%20Control%20Officer%20was%20sent%20to%C2%A0Vinesh's%20residence%20in%20Sonipat%20in%20Haryana%20on%20September%209%2C%20at%20the%20time%20specified%20by%20her%2C%20that%20she%20would%20be%20available%20there.%20But%C2%A0Vinesh%2C%20who%20is%20contesting%20the%20elections%20for%20the%20Haryana%20Assembly%2C%20was%20not%20available%20at%20her%20residence.%20This%2C%20NADA%20said%2C%20constitutes%20a%20whereabouts%20failure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVinesh%2C%20who%20made%20history%20for%20India%20by%20becoming%20the%20first%20female%20wrestler%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20final%20of%20the%20Women's%2050kg%20category%20in%20Paris%2C%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20reply%20to%20the%20notice%20within%2014%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20are%20hereby%20given%20a%20formal%20notice%20to%20notify%20you%20about%20the%20apparent%20failure%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20whereabouts%20requirements%20of%20the%20ADR%20and%20to%20invite%20you%20to%20make%20any%20comments%20before%20we%20come%20to%20a%20final%20decision%20on%20the%20matter.%20Please%20read%20this%20letter%20carefully%2C%20as%20it%20may%20have%20serious%20consequences%20for%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20NADA%20notice%2C%20a%20copy%20of%20which%20is%20available%20with%20IANS.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20IANS%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727939820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fm4rmntd_sv_625x300_03_October_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwrestling%2Fhe-cried-vinesh-phogat-accused-of-not-thanking-coach-mahavir-phogat-by-cousin-babita-phogat-6705862%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20India%20wrestler%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20was%20once%20again%20accused%20of%20not%20mentioning%20the%20name%20of%20uncle%20Mahavir%20Phogat%20in%20her%20'thank%20you'%20note%20following%20the%20disqualification%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fwrestling%2Fhe-cried-vinesh-phogat-accused-of-not-thanking-coach-mahavir-phogat-by-cousin-babita-phogat-6705862%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BPCL%20and%20Mumbai%20Port%20Authority%20to%20launch%20India's%20first%20green%20fuel%20ecosystem%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22