r%20remark%20on%20the%20divorce%20of%20celebrity%20couple%20Naga%20Chaitanya%20and%20Samantha%20Ruth%20Prabhu%2C%20Telangana%20Minister%20Konda%20Surekha%20apologised%20to%20the%20actors%20and%20their%20families%2C%20but%20did%20not%20back%20down%20from%20her%20allegations%20against%20Bharat%20Rashtra%20Samithi%20leader%20KT%20Rama%20Rao.%20She%20also%20stressed%20that%20Mr%20Rao%2C%20also%20known%20as%20KTR%2C%20must%20apologise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Surekha%20has%20alleged%20that%20KTR%2C%20a%20former%20minister%2C%20tapped%20the%20phones%20of%20actresses%20and%20blackmailed%20them.%20In%20this%20connection%2C%20she%20said%20he%20was%20behind%20the%20divorce%20of%20Samantha%20Ruth%20Prabhu%20and%20Naga%20Chaitanya.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20KT%20Rama%20Rao%20because%20of%20whom%20(actress)%20Samantha's%20divorce%20happened...%20He%20was%20a%20minister%20at%20that%20time%20and%20used%20to%20tap%20the%20phones%20of%20the%20actresses%20and%20then%20find%20their%20weaknesses%20to%20blackmail%20them...%20He%20used%20to%20make%20them%20drug%20addicts%20and%20then%20do%20this...%20Everyone%20knows%20this%2C%20Samantha%2C%20Naga%20Chaitanya%2C%20his%20family%20--%20everybody%20is%20aware%20that%20such%20a%20thing%20happened%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20sparked%20a%20massive%20row.%20Both%20Samantha%20Ruth%20Prabhu%20and%20Naga%20Chaitanya%20are%20top%20actors.%20Naga%20Chaitanya%20also%20belongs%20to%20the%20Akkineni%20family%2C%20among%20the%20most%20influential%20families%20in%20the%20Telugu%20film%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENagarjuna%20Akkineni%2C%20his%20father%20and%20veteran%20actor%2C%20responded%20sharply%20to%20the%20minister's%20remarks.%20%26quot%3BI%20strongly%20condemn%20the%20comments%20of%20the%20Honorable%20Minister%20Mrs.%20Konda%20Surekha.%20Don't%20use%20the%20lives%20of%20movie%20stars%20who%20stay%20away%20from%20politics%20to%20criticize%20your%20opponents.%20Please%20respect%20other%20people's%20privacy.%20As%20a%20woman%20in%20a%20responsible%20position%2C%20your%20comments%20and%20accusations%20against%20our%20family%20are%20completely%20irrelevant%20and%20false.%20I%20request%20you%20to%20withdraw%20your%20comments%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaga%20Chaitanya%20and%20Samanth%20Ruth%20Prabhu%20responded%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaga%20Chaitanya%20said%20the%20decision%20of%20a%20divorce%20is%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20most%20painful%20and%20unfortunate%20life%20decisions%20one%20has%20to%20make%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20a%20lot%20of%20thought%2C%20a%20mutual%20decision%20was%20made%20by%20me%20and%20my%20former%20spouse%20to%20part%20ways.%20It%20was%20a%20decision%20made%20in%20peace%2C%20owing%20to%20our%20different%20life%20goals%20and%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20moving%20forward%20with%20respect%20and%20dignity%20as%20two%20mature%20adults.%20However%2C%20there%20have%20been%20various%20baseless%20and%20completely%20ridiculous%20gossips%20on%20the%20matter%20so%20far.%20I%20have%20remained%20silent%20all%20this%20while%20out%20of%20deep%20respect%20for%20my%20earlier%20spouse%20as%20well%20as%20my%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday%2C%20the%20claim%20made%20by%20Minister%20Konda%20surekha%20garu%20is%20not%20only%20false%2C%20it%20is%20absolutely%20ridiculous%20and%20unacceptable.%20Women%20deserve%20to%20be%20supported%20and%20respected.%20Taking%20advantage%20and%20exploiting%20the%20personal%20life%20decisions%20of%20celebrities%20for%20the%20sake%20of%20media%20headlines%20is%20shameful%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESamantha%20Ruth%20Prabhu%20said%20it%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20courage%20and%20strength%20for%20a%20woman%20to%20survive%20in%20a%20glamorous%20industry%20where%20women%20are%20more%20often%20than%20not%20treated%20as%20props.%20%26quot%3BKonda%20Surekha%20Garu%2C%20I%20am%20proud%20of%20what%20this%20journey%20turned%20me%20into%20please%20don't%20tri