0driving%20the%20whole%20agenda%20from%20behind%20the%20scenes.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAffiliate%20NGOs%20such%20as%20Samvad%20were%20chosen%20for%20funding%20as%20Affiliate%20NGOs%20on%20the%20condition%20that%20they%20would%20allow%20Oxfam%20India%20%E2%80%9Ccomplete%20freedom%20to%20plan%20the%20program%20and%20staffing%20in%20manner%20they%20want.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBelow%20is%20an%20email%20excerpt%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20CBI%20FIR.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F5ov3agh8_oxfam-_625x300_03_October_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20diagram%20below%20is%20replicated%20from%20the%20CBI%20FIR.%20It%20outlines%20the%20roles%20and%20responsibilities%20of%20each%20part%20of%20the%20new%20structure.%20XXX%20indicates%20Oxfam%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F1l91vu98_oxfam_625x300_03_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBelow%20is%20an%20email%20excerpt%20that%20shows%20the%20possible%20names%20for%20the%20FPCs%20that%20were%20to%20be%20created%20by%20Oxfam%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fh705ooog_oxfam_625x300_03_October_24.png%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3E3.%20Plans%20to%20pressurise%20the%20Indian%20government%20through%20foreign%20governments%20%26amp%3B%20foreign%20institutions%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20type%3D%5C%22disc%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOxfam%20India%20was%20planning%20to%20use%20its%20influence%20with%20the%20World%20Bank%2C%20IMF%2C%20European%20Union%2C%20US%20State%20Department%2C%20Asian%20Development%20Bank%20and%20a%20clutch%20of%20European%20governments%20to%20put%20pressure%20on%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20renew%20its%20FCRA%20registration.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20type%3D%5C%22disc%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20Irish%20embassy%20was%20also%20approached%20by%20Oxfam%20India%20by%20Amitabh%20Behar%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20get%20the%20Ireland%20government%20to%20lean%20on%20India%20to%20renew%20FCRA.%20The%20excerpt%20of%20the%20email%20is%20below.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F05hifaag_oxfam_625x300_03_October_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E4.%C2%A0%3Cb%3ESuspicious%20donations%20from%20huge%20number%20of%20foreign%20individuals%C2%A0%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20type%3D%5C%22disc%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStrangely%2C%20a%20large%20number%20of%20donations%20have%20come%20in%20to%20Oxfam's%20FCRA%20account%20from%20individuals%20abroad.%20Even%20stranger%20is%20that%20the%20amounts%20round%20off%20perfectly%20when%20converted%20into%20Indian%20rupees.%20And%20a%20large%20number%20of%20individuals%20have%20donated%20the%20exact%20same%20amount.%20Below%20is%20a%20sample%20of%20the%20individual%20donations%20from%20abroad.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2F1hbbmet8_oxfam_625x300_03_October_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20type%3D%5C%22disc%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20amount%20of%20money%20donated%20by%20foreign%20individuals%20via%20the%20FCRA%20route%20is%20suspiciously%20high.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20British%20citizen%20by%20name%20Banwari%20Lal%20had%20gifted%20Oxfam%20India%20immovable%20property%20in%20Haryana%20in%202020.%20Oxfam%20India%20sold%20it%20for%20Rs%204%20crore%20but%20showed%20the%20value%20of%20the%20land%20as%20Rs%202.46%20crore%20only.%20This%20has%20raised%20suspicions%20about%20evasion%20of%20stamp%20duty.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cb%3EAbout%20Oxfam%20India%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmitabh%20Behar%20was%20the%20CEO%20of%20Oxfam%20India%20and%20was%20a%20former%20Executive%20Director%20of%20the%20National%20Foundation%20for%20India.%20Behar%20is%20a%20mentee%20of%20Salil%20Shetty%20who%20was%2C%20until%20recently%2C%20Vice%20President%20%E2%80%93%20Global%20Operations%20in%20Soros'%20Open%20Society%20Foundations%20(OSF).%20The%20organisations%20led%20by%20Behar%20have%20been%20the%20recipients%20of%20major%20funding%20from%20Soros'%20Open%20Society%20Foundations%20(OSF)%20as%20well%20as%20other%20foreign%20NGOs%20that%20are%20funded%20by%20the%20OSF.%C2%A0Behar%20is%20said%20to%20have%20gone%20abroad%20shortly%20after%20the%20CBI%20raided%20the%20NGO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENGOs%20are%20explicitly%20forbidden%20from%20sub-funding%20other%20NGOs%20%E2%80%93%20they%20must%20use%20the%20donations%20they%20receive%20only%20for%20the%20stated%20purpose%20that%20they%20have%20been%20formed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Oxfam%20has%20sub-funded%20a%20host%20of%20other%20NGOs.%20Here%20are%20some%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20type%3D%5C%22circle%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ECentre%20for%20Equity%20Studies%20led%20by%20Harsh%20Mander%2C%20a%20former%20member%20of%20Sonia%20Gandhi's%20National%20Advisory%20Council%20who%20was%20also%20recently%20in%20the%20running%20for%20a%20Nobel.%20This%20organisation%20has%20received%20Rs%201.2%20crore%20from%20Oxfam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20type%3D%5C%22circle%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ELegal%20Initiative%20for%20Forest%20and%20Environment%20(LIFE)%20which%20was%20founded%20by%20advocate%20Ritwick%20Dutta.%20Dutta%20was%20legal%20counsel%20for%20Fathima%20Babu%2C%20one%20of%20the%20leaders%20of%20the%20anti-Sterlite%20protests%20in%20Thoothukudi%20in%202018.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20type%3D%5C%22circle%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAssociation%20for%20Rural%20and%20Urban%20Needy%20(ARUN)%20in%20Telangana%20which%20is%20run%20by%20Bezwada%20Wilson.%20Partners%20of%20Oxfam%20in%20ARUN%20include%20the%20Fund%20For%20Global%20Human%20Rights%2C%20a%20Washington%20DC%20based%20organisation%20for%20building%20activism%20and%20protest%20groups%20across%20the%20world.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20type%3D%5C%22circle%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESwadhikar%20or%20National%20Campaign%20on%20Dalit%20Human%20Rights%20(NCDHR)%2C%20founded%20in%201998%20and%20now%20led%20by%20Paul%20Divakar%20Namala.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20type%3D%5C%22circle%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EOxfam%20India%20also%20granted%20Rs%201.4%20crore%20to%20the%20Centre%20for%20Social%20Equity%20and%20Inclusion%20(CSEI)%20between%202016-17%20and%202020-21%20as%20shown%20in%20their%20FCRA%20filings%20with%20the%20Indian%20government.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOxfam%20India%20itself%20has%2C%20as%20its%20donors%2C%20the%20Malala%20Fund.%20The%20Malala%20Fund%20is%20another%20well-known%20fund%20that%20donates%20to%20promote%20education%20for%20girls%20and%20is%3Ca%20data-linkindex%3D%5C%225%5C%22%20data-auth%3D%5C%22Verified%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fapc01.safelinks.protection.outlook.com%2F%3Furl%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252F2021.malala.org%252Four-donors%26data%3D05%257C02%257CPushkarT%2540ndtv.com%257C67da5b2a3b6d4d3d387208dce36ba5d8%257C89e0013190cd478790cc5ded788d77de%257C0%257C0%257C638635298735864958%257CUnknown%257CTWF