oted%20tradition%20steeped%20in%20history%2C%20legend%2C%20and%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20century-old%20custom%2C%20men%20dress%20up%20as%20women%20to%20atone%20for%20a%20curse%20placed%20on%20their%20ancestors%20by%20Sadu%20Mata%2C%20a%20woman%20whose%20story%20has%20been%20passed%20down%20through%20generations.%20According%20to%20local%20belief%2C%20over%20200%20years%20ago%2C%20a%20woman%20named%20Saduben%20sought%20protection%20from%20the%20men%20of%20the%20Barot%20community%20when%20a%20Mughal%20nobleman%20demanded%20her%20as%20a%20concubine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadly%2C%20the%20men%20did%20not%20defend%20her%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20tragic%20loss%20of%20her%20child.%20In%20her%20grief%20and%20anger%2C%20Saduben%20cursed%20the%20men%2C%20declaring%20that%20their%20future%20generations%20would%20suffer%20as%20cowards%2C%20and%20committed%20'sati'.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESadu%20Mata%20Ni%20Pol%2C%20which%20houses%20over%201%2C000%20residents%2C%20comes%20alive%20on%20the%20night%20of%20Ashtami.%20The%20pol%2C%20filled%20with%20narrow%20lanes%20and%20old-style%20homes%2C%20is%20a%20living%20relic%20of%20Ahmedabad's%20heritage.%20Crowds%20gather%20to%20witness%20men%20in%20sarees%2C%20twirling%20gracefully%20to%20the%20beats%20of%20Sheri%20Garba%2C%20a%20folk%20dance%20passed%20down%20through%20the%20generations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20temple%20was%20erected%20to%20appease%20Sadu%20Mata's%20spirit%20and%20lift%20the%20curse.%20Every%20year%2C%20on%20the%20night%20of%20Ashtami%2C%20men%20from%20the%20community%20gather%20at%20Sadu%20Mata%20Ni%20Pol%2C%20don%20sarees%2C%20and%20perform%20Garba%20as%20an%20act%20of%20penance.%20This%20custom%2C%20still%20alive%20today%2C%20draws%20crowds%20from%20all%20over%20the%20city%2C%20curious%20to%20witness%20this%20powerful%20display%20of%20tradition%20and%20devotion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20modern%20interpretations%20may%20associate%20the%20act%20of%20men%20dressing%20as%20women%20with%20bending%20gender%20norms%2C%20for%20the%20Barot%20community%2C%20it%20is%20a%20symbolic%20gesture%20of%20humility%20and%20respect.%20The%20ritual%20is%20believed%20to%20not%20only%20atone%20for%20the%20sins%20of%20the%20past%20but%20also%20to%20honour%20the%20blessings%20granted%20by%20Sadu%20Mata.%20Men%20who%20have%20prayed%20for%20personal%20wishes%20--%20be%20it%20success%20in%20business%2C%20good%20health%2C%20or%20the%20birth%20of%20a%20child%20--%20participate%20in%20this%20ritual%20to%20give%20thanks%20when%20their%20prayers%20are%20answered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Barot%20community%20of%20Gujarat%20is%20traditionally%20known%20for%20its%20role%20as%20genealogists%2C%20storytellers%2C%20and%20chroniclers%20for%20various%20communities.%20They%20particularly%20document%20family%20histories%20and%20preserve%20oral%20traditions.%20Historically%2C%20they%20served%20as%20keepers%20of%20genealogical%20records%2C%20especially%20for%20Rajput%20and%20Kshatriya%20families%2C%20and%20were%20integral%20to%20passing%20down%20cultural%20and%20religious%20stories%20through%20generations.%20In%20addition%20to%20their%20genealogical%20duties%2C%20they%20often%20performed%20during%20festivals%2C%20reciting%20epics%20and%20folk%20tales.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThough%20their%20traditional%20roles%20have%20evolved%20with%20time%2C%20the%20Barot%20community%20remains%20an%20important%20part%20of%20Gujarat's%20cultural%20heritage%2C%20particularly%20visible%20during%20festivals%20like%20Navratri%2C%20where%20their%20unique%20customs%20are%20still%20practiced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20participant%20shared%20that%20he%20has%20been%20wearing%20a%20saree%20for%20the%20past%20five%20years%20to%20show%20gratitude%20to%20Sadu%20Mata.%20After%20wishing%20for%20prosperity%20in%20his%20business%20and%20the%20blessing%20of%20a%20son%2C%20he%20felt%20that%20the%20goddess%20had%20been%20kind%20to%20him.%20For%20him%2C%20this%20tradition%20serves%20as%20a%20meaningful%20connection%20to%20their%20roots%2C%20allowing%20the%20community%20to%20express%20thanks%20for%20the%20blessings%20they%20receive%20in%20their%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tradition%2C%20however%2C%20isn't%20just%20about%20appeasing%20the%20curse.%20For%20many%2C%20it's%20about%20honouring%20the%20goddess%20they%20believe%20has%20protected%20and%20blessed%20their%20families%20for%20centuries.%20The%20pol%20transforms%20into%20a%20devotion%20site%2C%20with%20men%20of%20all%20ages%20paying%20homage%20to%20Sadu%20Mata%2C%20dressed%20in%20vibrant%20sarees%2C%20as%20an%20act%20of%20faith.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAhmedabad%2C%20India's%20first%20UNESCO%20World%20Heritage%20City%2C%20is%20known%20for%20its%20rich%20history%20and%20traditions.%20The%20ritual%20of%20men%20performing%20Garba%20in%20sarees%20is%20just%20one%20of%20the%20many%20ways%20the%20city%20preserves%20its%20cultural%20heritage.%20Nestled%20among%20the%20184%20pols%20of%20the%20old%20city%2C%20Sadu%20Mata%20Ni%20Pol%20stands%20as%20a%20testament%20to%20the%20resilience%20and%20devotion%20of%20the%20Barot%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1727933940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-10%2Fjc44ntv8_men-do-garba_625x300_03_October_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnavratri-2024-in-ahmedabad-men-dress-up-as-women-and-perform-garba-6705054%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20the%20Navratri%20festivities%20commence%20across%20the%20country%20on%20Thursday%20(October%201)%2C%20a%20unique%20tradition%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20Ahmedabad's%20old%20city%20draws%20everyone's%20attention.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnavratri-2024-in-ahmedabad-men-dress-up-as-women-and-perform-garba-6705054%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C