nth%20crypto-focused%20%26quot%3Bschool%26quot%3B%20for%20adults%20in%20nearby%20Malaysia.%20There%2C%20students%20would%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbalajis.com%2Fp%2Fnetwork-school%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBlueprint-inspired%20workouts%20and%20meals%3C%2Fa%3E%20led%20by%20Johnson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20summit%20was%20billed%20as%20possibly%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FDontDieSummit%2Fstatus%2F1831717503883714756%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20most%20important%20day%20of%20your%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20talks%20were%20less%20in-depth%20than%20I%20had%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I'm%20no%20longevity%20expert%2C%20the%20things%20discussed%20didn't%20feel%20all%20that%20new%20or%20novel.%20Most%20of%20Johnson's%20advice%20is%20as%20old-school%20as%20it%20gets%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eeat%2C%20sleep%2C%20and%20exercise%20well%20%E2%80%94%20although%20the%20other%20talks%20and%20exhibition%20booths%20were%20focused%20on%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Epractices%20like%20blood%20testing%20that%20cost%20a%20pretty%20penny.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221f397b7c-2761-46cc-9816-90495a03bf36%5C%22%3EThe%20quest%20for%20immortality%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EImmortality%20has%20always%20been%20the%20stuff%20of%20science%20fiction%2C%20but%20it%20seems%20like%20mankind%20might%20just%20turn%20it%20into%20a%20reality%20with%20some%20help%20from%20technology%20and%20AI%3Cstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20or%20so%20Johnson%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-titans-sam-altman-turning-to-anti-aging-drugs-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etech%20titans%3C%2Fa%3E%20believe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20composite%20image%20of%20Bryan%20Johnson%20in%20a%20black%20shirt%20with%20cropped%20hair%20and%20him%20in%20a%20metallic%20green%20shirt%20with%20longer%20hair.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%