%20Mountain%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Yunnan%2C%20China%2C%20where%20we%20had%20to%20fly%20all%20our%20guests%20in%20and%20build%20tents%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20snowcapped%20mountaintop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEntertainment%20is%20another%20key%20expense.%20It's%20not%20uncommon%20for%20clients%20to%20request%20a%20performance%20from%20world-renowned%20artists%2C%20like%20in%20the%20recent%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fambani-pre-wedding-celebration-with-justin-bieber-performance-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmbani%3C%2Fa%3E%20wedding.%20Whether%20it's%20a%20singer%2C%20a%20band%2C%20or%20even%20a%20magician%2C%20these%20acts%20can%20cost%20up%20a%20significant%20sum%20for%20just%20a%20few%20hours%20of%20entertainment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d66b8393-8c83-45eb-9f16-fba029eb465a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESatisfying%20personal%20tastes%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there%20are%20food%20and%20beverage%20costs%2C%20which%20can%20vary%20greatly%20depending%20on%20the%20client.%20Not%20every%20wealthy%20family%20wants%20to%20serve%20the%20most%20expensive%20wines%20in%20the%20world.%20For%20some%2C%20it's%20about%20sentimental%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20had%20clients%20who%20preferred%20to%20fly%20in%20chefs%20from%20their%20favorite%20restaurant%20or%20home%20country%20to%20prepare%20a%20familiar%20meal%20rather%20than%20going%20for%20extravagance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20also%20helped%20a%20client%20%E2%80%94%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-states-with-best-wineries-vineyards-from-a-sommelier%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewine%3C%2Fa%3E%20aficionado%20%E2%80%94%20locate%20and%20purchase%20a%20vineyard%20so%20he%20could%20serve%20wine%20with%20his%20own%20label%20at%20the%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20get%20uncommon%20requests%20like%20this%2C%20it's%20important%20that%20we%20don't%20flinch%20and%20help%20our%20clients%20however%20we%20can.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2230090f0d-6b08-4ebb-8fda-b93314d90a4f%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EYounger%20generation's%20focus%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMultiple%20generations%20are%20also%20involved%2C%20each%20with%20their%20own%20expectations%20for%20the%20wedding%20day.%20For%20the%20older%20generation%2C%20upholding%20traditions%20is%20essential.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20some%20traditional%20Chinese%20weddings%20have%20six%20different%20tea%20ceremonies%20to%20honor%20the%20family's%20elders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chinese%20betrothal%20gifts%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66f502b4f9f6733e4bdfad06%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22398%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGifts%20presented%20at%20a%20traditional%20Chinese%20betrothal%20ceremony.%3Cp%3EThe%20Atelier%20%26amp%3B%20Co%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20younger%20generation%20is%20more%20focused%20on%20creating%20intimate%2C%20personalized%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20my%20clients%20opt%20for%20multiple%20events%20%E2%80%94%20a%20massive%20celebration%20at%20home%20to%20honor%20family%20traditions%2C%20followed%20by%20a%20smaller%2C%20more%20intimate%20destination%20wedding%20for%20their%20close%20friends%20and%20loved%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20I've%20noticed%20a%20shift%20in%20Asian%20weddings%20whereby%20younger%20generations%20emphasize%20upholding%20traditions%20in%20their%20weddings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20no%20longer%20just%20about%20the%20Western-style%20white%20gown%20and%20vow%20exchanges.%20Couples%20incorporate%20traditional%20touches%2C%20unique%20to%20their%20own%20cultural%20roots%2C%20into%20the%20grand%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20it's%20common%20for%20the%20bride%20to%20have%20several%20wardrobe%20changes%20besides%20the%20standard%20white%20gown.%20For%20different%20events%2C%20she%20might%20wear%20other%20gowns%20reflective%20of%20her%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20been%20inspiring%20to%20see%20this%20because%20it%20differentiates%20the%20weddings%20we%20do%20here%20in%20Asia%20from%20those%20happening%20worldwide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20had%20the%20opportunity%20to%20incorporate%20cultural%20aspects%20into%20weddings%2C%20from%20traditional%20Indian%20ceremonies%20to%20Moroccan%20and%20Bangladeshi%20elements%2C%20making%20these%20events%20stand%20out%20and%20celebrate%20the%20rich%20traditions%20of%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20would%20flock%20to%20Lake%20Como%20or%20France%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foverrated-wedding-traditions-according-to-wedding-planners-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edestination%20weddings%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20I've%20always%20believed%20that%20choosing%20a%20location%20tied%20to%20one's%20culture%20makes%20the%20experience%20even%20more%20special.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20the%20wedding%20we%20planned%20on%20the%20top%20of%20the%20Snow%20Jade%20Dragon%20Mountain%20in%20China%20was%20for%20a%20bride%20with%20deep%20cultural%20ties%20to%20the%20region.%20We%20involved%20local%20villagers%20in%20preparing%20a%20traditional%20feast%2C%20creating%20handmade%20furniture%2C%20and%20performing%20local%20songs%2C%20making%20the%20event%20beautiful%2C%20deeply%20meaningful%2C%20and%20authentic%20to%20the%20bride's%20heritage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20working%20around%20high-net-worth%20individuals%3F%20Email%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Alwee%40insider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Elwee%40insider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-wealthy-couples-spend-money-wedding-planner-tradition-venue-entertainment-2024-10%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Inside