hat%20he%20was%20planning%20on%20having%20the%20same%20conversation%20with%20Hannah.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20moment%2C%20it%20seems%20like%20the%20issue%20is%20going%20to%20resolve%20itself%20after%20Hannah%20tells%20Leo%20in%20episode%20three%20that%20she%20and%20Nick%20D.%2C%20another%20cast%20member%2C%20have%20confessed%20their%20love%20to%20each%20other.%20Leo%20doesn't%20take%20the%20breakup%20attempt%20well%2C%20demanding%20to%20know%20whether%20Hannah%20would%20agree%20to%20marry%20him%20if%20he%20asks%20in%20that%20instant%20and%20bringing%20her%20to%20tears.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20another%20meeting%20in%20episode%20four%2C%20Hannah%20and%20Leo%20agree%20to%20end%20their%20relationship%20after%20Hannah%20tells%20him%20that%20she%20has%20stronger%20feelings%20for%20Nick.%20Leo%20asks%20Hannah%20to%20tell%20Brittany%20that%20their%20split%20was%20mutual%2C%20so%20that%20Brittany%20doesn't%20think%20that%20she's%20his%20second%20choice.%20Hannah%20declines%20%E2%80%94%20but%20%3Cem%3Edoes%3C%2Fem%3E%20tell%20Brittany%20that%20he%20asked%20her%20to%20do%20so.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20episode%20four%2C%20Brittany%20tells%20Leo%20that%20she's%20still%20%26quot%3Bhurt%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20way%20he%20handled%20his%20relationships%20with%20her%20and%20Hannah.%20Leo%20attempts%20to%20propose%2C%20but%20Brittany%20turns%20him%20down%20and%20tells%20him%20to%20ask%20again.%20In%20episode%20five%2C%20he%20tries%20again%2C%20and%20she%20says%20yes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20two%20meet%20at%20their%20reveal%2C%20however%2C%20the%20tension%20is%20palpable.%20Brittany%20still%20can't%20tell%20Leo%20that%20she%20loves%20him%2C%20and%20the%20pair%20agrees%20that%20if%20they%20aren't%20selected%20for%20the%20show's%20couples%20trip%20to%20Mexico%2C%20they%20will%20travel%20to%20Miami%20together%20instead.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMexico%20wasn't%20meant%20to%20be%2C%20and%20neither%20was%20this%20couple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBrittany%20%26amp%3B%20Leo%20were%20not%20one%20of%