se%2C%20you'll%20be%20making%20frequent%20trips%20to%20the%20trash%20can%20while%20cleaning.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20worth%20noting%20that%20some%20newer%20cordless%20vacuums%20have%20self-emptying%20bases.%20When%20you%20place%20the%20vacuum%20back%20on%20its%20dock%2C%20it%20automatically%20empties%20the%20on-board%20dust%20bin%20into%20the%20base.%20This%20saves%20you%20from%20having%20to%20empty%20the%20vacuum%20manually%20and%20helps%20to%20keep%20the%20dustbin%20clean%20and%20dust-free.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EAttachments%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20use%20your%20cordless%20vacuums%20to%20clean%20different%20areas%20of%20your%20home%2C%20you%20may%20want%20to%20look%20for%20a%20model%20with%20special%20tools%20and%20attachments.%20Some%20options%20have%20separate%20floorheads%20for%20carpeting%20vs.%20hard%20floors%2C%20while%20others%20come%20with%20accessories%20like%20crevice%20tools%2C%20dusting%20brushes%2C%20and%20upholstery%20cleaners.%20It's%20also%20worth%20considering%20how%20you'll%20store%20the%20attachments%20%E2%80%94%20some%20vacuum%20docks%20have%20slots%20for%20accessories%2C%20which%20is%20handy%20for%20keeping%20everything%20organized.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EDocking%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EYour%20cordless%20vacuum%20will%20need%20to%20be%20charged%20after%20each%20use%2C%20and%20many%20models%20come%20with%20convenient%20freestanding%20or%20wall-mounted%20docking%20stations.%20When%20you%20place%20the%20vacuum%20back%20in%20the%20dock%2C%20it%20automatically%20recharges%20so%20it%20will%20be%20ready%20for%20next%20use.%20If%20the%20vacuum%20you%20choose%20doesn't%20come%20with%20a%20dock%2C%20you'll%20likely%20need%20to%20plug%20it%20in%20manually%20or%20remove%20the%20battery%20to%20charge%20it%20between%20uses%2C%20which%20is%20a%20bit%20more%20cumbersome.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cspan%3EBudget%3A%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cspan%3ECordless%20vacuums%20can%20vary%20significantly%20in%20price%2C%20ranging%20from%20%24100%20to%20upward%20of%20%241%2C000%20for%20premium%20models.%20If%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20supplementary%20cleaning%20tool%2C%20a%20more%20budget-friendly%20option%20will%20generally%20be%20fine%20for%20light-duty%20cleaning%2C%20but%20if%20you%20want%20a%20cordless%20model%20to%20be%20your%20home's%20primary%20vacuum%2C%20you%20may%20need%20to%20spend%20a%20bit%20more%20to%20get%20powerful%20suction%20and%20longer%20battery%20life.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHow%20we%20test%20cordless%20vacuum%20cleaners%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Various%20materials%2C%20like%20cat%20litter%2C%20flour%2C%20cheerios%20cereal%2C%20and%20ground%20coffee%2C%20are%20scattered%20on%20the%20ground%20to%20test%20the%20best%20cordless%20vacuums%20in%202022.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6054f4cecad7d300183f81d9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EConnie%20Chen%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20tested%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20cordless%20vacuum%20cleaners%20from%20top%20brands%20like%20Shark%2C%20Dyson%20and%20Tineco%2C%20and%20our%20testers%20evaluate%20each%20model%20on%20the%20following%20criteria%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Cleaning%20performance%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20most%20important%20factor%20when%20selecting%20a%20vacuum%20is%20its%20cleaning%20abilities%2C%20so%20we%20put%20each%20model%20through%20a%20series%20of%20tests%20to%20see%20how%20well%20it%20can%20pick%20up%20different%20types%20of%20debris.%20We%20measure%20out%2030%20grams%20of%20flour%2C%20ground%20coffee%2C%20Cheerios%2C%20and%20cat%20litter%2C%20then%20vacuum%20up%20each%20one%2C%20weighing%20the%20vacuum%20to%20see%20if%20it%20truly%20picked%20up%20all%20the%20debris.%20We%20repeat%20these%20tests%20on%20both%20hard%20floors%20and%20carpeting.%20We%20also%20use%20each%20vacuum%20to%20clean%20up%20pet%20hair%2C%20noting%20whether%20it%20gets%20wrapped%20around%20the%20brushroll%2C%20and%20we%20try%20out%20any%20attachments%20that%20come%20with%20the%20vacuum.%20I%20tested%20each%20of%20the%20vacuums%20against%20five%20materials%20(flour%2C%20ground%20coffee%2C%20cat%20litter%2C%20whole%20Cheerios%2C%20and%20dog%20hair)%20on%20three%20different%20surfaces%20(carpet%2Frug%2C%20hardwood%2C%20and%20tile).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20example%20of%20one%20of%20the%20test%20results%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Ccolgroup%3E%3Ccol%3E%3Ccol%3E%3Ccol%3E%3C%2Fcolgroup%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3EFlour%20test%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3EHardfloor%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3ECarpet%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3EShark%20Stratos%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E94%25-%20Most%20of%20the%20flour%20was%20picked%20up%20on%20the%20first%20swipe%2C%20but%20there%20were%20visible%20streaks%20and%20small%20clumps%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E100%25%20-%20Sucked%20up%20all%20particles%20completely%20on%20Auto%3B%20struggled%20with%20eco%20mode.%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3ELevoit%20LVAC-200%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E100%25%20-%20Fully%20picked%20up%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20rowspan%3D%5C%221%5C%22%3E94%25%20-%20A%20little%20residue%20left%20over%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Battery%20life%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20battery%20life%20of%20cordless%20vacuums%20often%20varies%20significantly%20from%20the%20marketed%20runtime%2C%20so%20we%