e%20hybrid%20powertrain%20is%20called%20upon%20to%20deliver%20the%20grunt%20needed%20for%20highway%20on-ramps%20or%20any%20real%20acceleration.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStep%20on%20the%20gas%20and%20the%20serenity%20of%20the%20cabin%20is%20harshly%20interrupted%20by%20the%20loud%2C%20intrusive%20drone%20of%20its%20four-cylinder%20engine%20straining%20to%20propel%20the%204%2C600%20lb%20SUV.%20It%20just%20feels%20underpowered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.motortrend.com%2Fcars%2Ftoyota%2Fhighlander%2F2024%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMotor%20Trend%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%202024%20Highlander%20Hybrid%20can%20accelerate%20from%200%20to%2060%20in%208.4%20seconds%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20those%20seconds%20can%20be%20painful%20on%20your%20ears.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20the%20overall%20experience%20particularly%20surprising%20as%20my%20daily%20driver%20is%20also%20powered%20by%20Toyota's%20hybrid%20system%20with%20a%202.5-liter%20four-cylinder%20engine%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20make%20nearly%20the%20racket%20this%20thing%20does.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20it's%20disappointing%20to%20know%20that%20Toyota%20is%20absolutely%20capable%20of%20delivering%20the%20refined%20powertrain%20the%20Highlander%20Hybrid%20deserves%20but%20hasn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20interior%20of%20my%20Highlander%20Hybrid%20Platinum%20test%20car%20was%20impressive.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20front%20dash%20of%20a%202024%20Toyota%20Highlander%20Hybrid%20Platinum%20SUV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fabe1e75c877a99b61ba95%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Highlander%20Hybrid%20Platinum's%20front%20dash.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Highlander%20cabin%20is%20a%20thoroughly%20enjoyable%20place%20to%20be.%20It's%20stylish%2C%20thoughtfully%20designed%2C%20and%20packed%20with%20handy%20storage%20nooks.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat's%20most%20impressive%20is%20the%20material%20and%20build%20quality.%20The%20plastic%20interior%20trim%20pieces%20felt%20substantial%2C%20and%20the%20entire%20cabin%20felt%20impeccably%20screwed%20together.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMy%20test%20car%20was%20covered%20in%20soft%2C%20rich%20tan%20leather%20that%20felt%20fit%20for%20a%20Lexus.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20tan%20leather%20front%20seats%20in%20a%202024%20Toyota%20Highlander%20Hybrid%20Platinum%20SUV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fab3e375c877a99b61b490%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Highlander%20Hybrid's%20heated%20and%20ventilated%20leather%20front%20seats.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBase%20LE%20trim%20Highlanders%20have%20fabric%20seats%2C%20while%20mid-grade%20models%20are%20trimmed%20in%20SofTex%20synthetic%20leather.%20Only%20XLE%20and%20Platinum%20grade%20models%2C%20like%20my%20tester%2C%20get%20leather%20upholstery.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20front%20of%20the%20driver%20is%20a%20heated%2C%20leather-wrapped%20steering%20wheel.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20black%20leather%20steering%20wheel%20in%20a%202024%20Toyota%20Highlander%20Hybrid%20Platinum%20SUV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fabde97518aa57bc9f32b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Highlander's%20steering%20wheel.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20layout%20of%20the%20steering%20wheel's%20media%20and%20driver's%20assistance%20feature%20controls%20are%20shared%20across%20other%20models%20in%20the%20Toyota%2FLexus%20lineup.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EInstead%20of%20a%20traditional%20gauge%20cluster%2C%20the%20Highlander%20comes%20with%20a%20digital%20instrument%20display.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222947%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20digital%20instrument%20display%20on%20the%20front%20dash%20of%20a%202024%20Toyota%20Highlander%20Hybrid%20Platinum%20SUV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fca6ba5ccfc192a5527632%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222210%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Highlander%20Hybrid's%20digital%20instrument%20display.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2012.3-inch%20digital%20display%20looks%20good%20and%20is%20configurable.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EPlatinum-grade%20Highlanders%20come%20with%20a%20head-up%20display.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221390%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20head-up%20display%20projected%20onto%20the%20windshield%20of%20a%202024%20Toyota%20Highlander%20Hybrid%20Platinum%20SUV%20parked%20on%20a%20street.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fc9bd39e0c5c2eeee9e789%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221043%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Highlander%20Hybrid's%20HUD.%3Cp%3EBenjamin%20Zhang%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2010-inch%20HUD%20gives%20drivers%20easy%20access%20to%20key%20information%2C%20such%20as%20speed%2C%20hybrid%20system%20status%2C%20and%20driver%20assistance%20status.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20focal%20point%20of%20the%20Highlander's%20front%20dash%20is%20its%2012.3-inch%20touchscreen.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222734%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20front%20dash%20and%20center%20console%20of%20a%202024%20Toyota%20Highlander%20Hybrid%20Platinum%20SUV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66fc9c327de5c8fd48348484%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222050%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Highlander%20Hybrid%20Platinum's%20front%20dash%20and%20center%