m%20in%20several%20government%20schemes.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Froshni-child-marriage-1727791803.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Froshni-child-marriage-1727791803-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Froshni-child-marriage-1727791803-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Froshni-child-marriage-1727791803-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F10%2Froshni-child-marriage-1727791803-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-368389%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERoshni%20also%20helps%20young%20girls%20with%20skill%20development%20by%20enrolling%20them%20in%20several%20government%20schemes.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5%20steps%20towards%20combatting%20child%20marriage%20in%20India%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERoshni%20assists%20families%20of%20girls%20in%20availing%20welfare%20schemes%20such%20as%20housing%20under%20Indira%20Awaas%20Yojana%20and%20ration%20cards%20for%20Below%20Poverty%20Line%20(BPL)%20households.%20She%20also%20helps%20them%20with%20skill%20development%20by%20enrolling%20them%20in%20the%20Kaushal%20Yuva%20Program%2C%20beauty%20parlours%2C%20and%20stitching%20centres%20so%20that%20they%20are%20no%20longer%20seen%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98burden%E2%80%99%20to%20the%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20this%20journey%20towards%20empowering%20young%20girls%20has%20not%20been%20easy%20for%20Roshni.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20been%20labelled%20characterless%20because%20I%20left%20my%20abusive%20husband.%20As%20I%20was%20unable%20to%20build%20a%20family%20of%20my%20own%2C%20people%20say%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20want%20other%20girls%20to%20settle%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%