gcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThrough%20the%20war%2C%20some%20people%20had%20acquired%20disabilities%20or%20become%20injured%2C%20including%20around%20300%20Deaf%20people%20who%20had%20become%20displaced.%20They%20were%20asking%20me%2C%20as%20a%20fellow%20Deaf%20person%2C%20for%20help.%20I%20was%20not%20aware%20of%20how%20to%20help%2C%20so%20I%20had%20a%20lot%20to%20learn%2C%20especially%20how%20to%20deal%20with%20post-traumatic%20stress%20disorder.%20Deaf%20people%20wanted%20to%20tell%20me%20their%20stories%20and%20what%20they%20went%20through.%20By%20being%20able%20to%20communicate%20with%20me%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20give%20them%20a%20message%20of%20love%20and%20reassurance%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20told%20UN%20Volunteers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20her%20one-and-a-half-year%20stint%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20Rupmani%20also%20took%20part%20in%20multiple%20initiatives%20with%20other%20UN%20agencies%20%E2%80%94%20including%20the%20Office%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20High%20Commissioner%20for%20Human%20Rights%20(OHCHR)%2C%20United%20Nations%20Children%E2%80%99s%20Fund%20(UNICEF)%2C%20and%20the%20United%20Nations%20Refugee%20Agency%20(UNHCR).%20It%20was%20a%20truly%20rewarding%20time%20for%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20she%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20facing%20numerous%20discouragements%2C%20I%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20embrace%20life%20as%20a%20series%20of%20risks%2C%20willing%20to%20try%20anything%20that%20came%20my%20way.%20I%20moved%20to%20Ukraine%20and%20travelled%20across%20Europe%2C%20where%20I%20was%20amazed%20by%20the%20robust%20access%20to%20sign%20language%20in%20other%20countries%2C%20especially%20the%20availability%20of%20technology%20like%20VRS.%20This%20exposure%20allowed%20me%20to%20learn%20and%20grow%20in%20ways%20I%20had%20never%20imagined.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESignAble%20for%20the%20Deaf%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp