g%20us%20launch%20the%20three%20zero%20waste%20villages%20of%20Darjeeling%2C%E2%80%9D%20Utsow%20acknowledges.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMeet%20the%20waste%20warriors%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20help%20of%20his%20team%2C%20Utsow%20has%20built%20an%20impressive%20waste%20treatment%20facility%20that%20segregates%20waste%20into%2053%20categories%20before%20treating%20or%20recycling%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20walk%20down%20the%20steps%20to%20reach%20the%20building%2C%20Snehal%20Sinalkar%2C%20who%20oversees%20the%20project%20as%20team%20lead%2C%20introduces%20me%20to%20their%20waste%20warriors%20%E2%80%94%20a%20group%20of%20chickens%2C%20two%20rabbits%20expecting%20new%20friends%20soon%2C%20and%20two%20guinea%20pigs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20at%20the%20composting%20pit%2C%20Snehal%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20has%20the%20capacity%20to%20process%20100%20kg%20of%20waste.%20So%2C%20we%20dump%20the%20waste%20here%2C%20and%20the%20chickens%20do%20their%20work.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201450px)%20100vw%2C%201450px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fted1-1727447257.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221450%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Waste-warriors%20at%20the%20Tieedi%20facility%20include%20a%20group%20of%20chickens%2C%20two%20rabbits%20expecting%20new%20friends%20soon%2C%20and%20two%20guinea%20pigs.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fted1-1727447257.jpg%201450w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fted1-1727447257-300x213.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fted1-1727447257-500x355.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fted1-1727447257-768x545.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fted1-1727447257-1200x852.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fted1-1727447257-150x106.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-367885%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221029%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EWaste%20warriors%20at%20the%20Tieedi%20facility%20include%20a%20group%20of%20chickens%2C%20two%20rabbits%20expecting%20new%20friends%20soon%2C%20and%20two%20guinea%20pigs.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnimal%20integration%20is%20a%20major%20part%20of%20permaculture.%20The%20chickens%20eat%20a%20lot%20of%20the%20biodegradable%20material%2C%20and%20then%20they%20poop.%20That%20works%20as%20a%20catalyst%20in%20processing%20the%20biodegradable%20material%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20also%20have%20another%20important%20role%20%E2%80%94%20aeration.%20This%20is%20crucial%20for%20maintaining%20moisture%20and%20oxygen%20levels%20in%20the%20compost%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20Aeration%20involves%20creating%20air%20pockets%20that%20allow%20enough%20oxygen%20to%20convert%20organic%20matter%20into%20compost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20entire%20collection%20and%20composting%20process%20is%20done%20manually.%20The%20sloping%20terrain%20is%20utilised%2C%20allowing%20waste%20to%20be%20placed%20at%20a%20facility%20uphill%20from%20where%20it%20gently%20rolls%20down%20to%20the%20composting%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EReviving%20a%20stream%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20planted%20about%20600%20trees%20in%20the%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20Utsow%20says%20when%20I%20ask%20him%20about%20the%20tiny%20river%20flowing%20through%20the%20compound.%20%E2%80%9CWe%E2%80%99ve%20also%20cut%20the%20hills%20into%20steps%20to%20allow%20water%20to%20recharge%20the%20soil%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20river%2C%20like%20several%20others%20flowing%20in%20the%20Shivaliks%2C%20is%20most%20active%20during%20the%20mon