%20Factory%20roof%20structure.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20what%20if%20there%20are%20mismatches%3F%20It%20only%20adds%20to%20the%20authenticity%20of%20the%20space%2C%20the%20architect%20believes.%20That%20being%20said%2C%20he%20adds%20that%20in%20places%20where%20it%20was%20necessitated%2C%20safety%20upgrades%20were%20made.%20These%20include%20structural%20reinforcements%20to%20the%20walls%20and%20roof.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-3_11zon-1726747460.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22IF.BE%20boasts%20five%20sections%20which%20include%20a%20fine-dining%20restaurant%2C%20a%20cafe%2C%20a%20space%20for%20exhibitions%2C%20a%20space%20for%20performances%20and%20a%20reading%20room%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-3_11zon-1726747460.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-3_11zon-1726747460-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-3_11zon-1726747460-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-3_11zon-1726747460-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-3_11zon-1726747460-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366752%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIF.BE%20boasts%20five%20sections%20which%20include%20a%20fine-dining%20restaurant%2C%20a%20cafe%2C%20a%20space%20for%20exhibitions%2C%20a%20space%20for%20performances%2C%20and%20a%20reading%20room%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20space%20that%20took%20the%20most%20amount%20of%20brainstorming%2C%20Malik%20shares%2C%20was%20the%20main%20Ice%20Factory%2C%20sub-station%2C%20cold%20storage%2C%20and%20the%20ice-cubing%20area.%20%E2%80%9CThese%20required%20intensive%20examination%20and%20surgical%20intervention%20through%20retrofits%20to%20stabilise%20crumbling%2C%20warped%2C%20and%20leaking%20walls%2C%20sagging%20roofs%20and%20trusses.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20in%20every%20adventure%20story%2C%20the%20most%20exciting%20part%20is%20when%20a%20treasure%20is%20discovered.%20When%20the%20team%20stumbled%20upon%20giant%20cooling%20coils%20that%20were%20once%20used%20to%20manufacture%20ice%2C%20they%20were%20thrilled.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1726747608.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20restoration%20process%20took%20a%20total%20of%20two%20years%20before%20IF.BE%20was%20deemed%20ready%20to%20host%20events%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1726747608.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1726747608-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1726747608-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1726747608-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fsustainable-architecture-4-1726747608-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-366757%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20restoration%20process%20took%20a%20total%20of%20two%20years%20before%20IF.BE%20was%20deemed%20ready%20to%20host%20events%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20have%20also%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F309116%2Fias-officer-anshul-gupta-efi-volunteers-restore-pond-wildlife-ujjain-madhya-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efeatured%20in%20the%20restoration%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20are%20embedded%20in%20the%20glass%20floor%20towards%20the%20entrance.%20Another%20treasure%20lay%20in%20uncovering%20the%20historic%20gantry%20that%20once%20facilitated%20the%20transport%20of%20ice%20slabs.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20room%20was%20a%20%E2%80%98giant%20ice%20tray%E2%80%99%20where%20ice%20was%20manufactured.%20There%20were%20four-foot-deep%20pits%20with%20refrigerant%20coils%20running%20alongside%20that%20would%20freeze%20the%20water%20in%20the%20pits.%20The%20massive%20ice%20blocks%20were%20then%20picked%20up%20using%20a%20crane%20and%20moved%20to%20an%20area%20where%20they%20would%20be%20cut%20and%20distributed%20for%20their%20final%20purpose.%E2%80%9D%20During%20restoration%2C%20the%20raised%20floor%20was%20wood%20panelled%20and%20can%20be%20opened%20to%20reveal%20the%20pits.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThrough%20the%20architect%E2%80%99s%20lens%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20almost%20as%20if%20time%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20ticked%20within%20the%20Ballard%20Estate%20neighbourhood%20of%20South%20Mumbai.%20With%20its%20neoclassical%20architecture%2C%20defunct%20railway%20station%2C%20which%20once%20saw%20a%20host%20of%20British%20passengers%20board%20steamers%2C%20and%20remnants%20of%20the%20colonial%20era%2C%20the%20South%20Bombay%20pincode%20is%20almost%20a%20bubble%20frozen%20in%20time.%20Copious%20amounts%20of%20ice%20were%20manufactured%20every%20day%2C%20which%20made%20their%20way%20from%20the%20factory%20to%20the%20restaurants%2C%20fish%20markets%20and%20vegetable%20markets%20across%20South%20Bombay.%3C%2