9s%20mind%20has%20touched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20walk%20down%20the%20lane%20of%20Hanif%20Kureshi%E2%80%99s%20work%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPoignant%E2%80%9D%20is%20how%20admirers%20of%20%E2%80%98Daku%E2%80%99s%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%98Cycle%20of%20Time%E2%80%99%20installation%20describe%20it%20to%20be.%20It%20has%20a%20profound%20impact%20on%20the%20viewer.%20Displayed%20at%20the%20India%20Art%20Architecture%20Design%20Biennale%20(IAADB)%20at%20the%20Red%20Fort%20in%20Delhi%20in%202023%2C%20the%20installation%20features%20a%20canopy%20of%20words%20%E2%80%98PAST%20IS%20PRESENT%20IS%20FUTURE%20IS%20PAST%E2%80%99%20in%20a%20trance-inducing%20sequence.%20The%20shadows%20they%20cast%20shift%20in%20tandem%20with%20the%20movement%20of%20the%20Sun%2C%20underscoring%20the%20elusive%20nature%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKureshi%E2%80%99s%20work%20combined%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F291305%2Faravani-art-project-bengaluru-helps-trans-community-tackle-stigma-earn-income%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebursts%20of%20colour%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20cheeky%20take%20on%20societal%20issues.%20This%20is%20evident%20in%20one%20of%20his%20works%20tracing%20back%20to%202014%2C%20specifically%20to%20the%20weeks%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20general%20election.%20Four%20large%20monochrome%20paste-ups%20of%20a%20middle%20finger%20marked%20with%20an%20indelible%20ink%20blot%2C%20and%20captioned%20with%20the%20Hindi%20phrase%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EMat%20Do%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Vote)%E2%80%99%20were%20placed%20across%20New%20Delhi.%20The%20graffiti%20was%20cheeky%2C%20compelling%20people%20who%20took%20it%20at%20face%20value%20to%20%E2%80%98go%20vote%E2%80%99%2C%20but%20compelling%20those%20who%20read%20between%20the%20lines%20to%20%E2%80%98not%20vote%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3